title: Transformers RID 2015 S01E06 720p [TankEngine]
description:
Better late than never, here's Transformers RID 2015 S01E06 in English! This is the first and only place I am uploading it. Please feel free to share it around but remember to give credit where credit is due.

Chapter markings are included for your convenience.

Please note that because of the way this is broadcast, it has been upscaled to 720p and so is not "true" 720p.

Video: 

720p @ 50fps (upscaled from 576i @ 25fps)
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, H.264

Audio:

MPEG-2 Stereo @ 48kHz
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, AAC

Please enjoy this show and make sure to check back next weekend for episode 4 and beyond!

N.B.:

The opening vocals have a split-second cut off the beginning (thanks, CN - it was broadcast this way). I was going to fix this but decided it was more effort than it was worth
